\par When vacancies happen in the Representation from any State, the Executive Authority thereof shall issue Writs of Election to fill such Vacancies.
\par The House of Representatives shall chuse their Speaker and other Officers; and shall have the sole Power of Impeachment. {\*\bkmkstart articleI3}{\*\bkmkend articleI3}
